xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gvp1703059102805.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gvp1703059102805.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gvp1703059102805.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kax1665703009534\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\"> $runmode (deprecated)\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"kax1665703009534___runmode_286055\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return an indication of how the form was started.</p>\n<div class=\"note important note_important\" id=\"kax1665703009534__note_w8823ab1b7b5_w8824ab1b7_w8825ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Important:</span> The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$runmode</span> function has been superseded by\n            <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$editmode</span>. </div>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"kax1665703009534__topic_d88658e1_d88659e1_d88660e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kax1665703009534__p_d88661e1_d88662e1_d88663e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$runmode</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kax1665703009534__topic_d59047e1_d59048e1_d59049e1_d59050e1_d59051e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d490080e75\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"kax1665703009534__table_d9551e1_d9552e1_d9553e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$runmode</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kax1665703009534__table_d9551e1_d9552e1_d9553e1__entry__1\">\n Value \n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kax1665703009534__table_d9551e1_d9552e1_d9553e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kax1665703009534__table_d9551e1_d9552e1_d9553e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kax1665703009534__table_d9551e1_d9552e1_d9553e1__entry__2\">\n The form can be used for all I/O purposes. All of these conditions are met:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kax1665703009534__li_d35423e1_d35424e1_d35425e1\">The form became active with an <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">edit</span> statement, or the exec operation is empty. in this case, Uniface behaves as if an <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">edit</span> statement were present.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kax1665703009534__li_d35426e1_d35427e1_d35428e1\">The form is not a Limited form.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kax1665703009534__li_d35429e1_d35430e1_d35431e1\">The form was started by one of these methods:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kax1665703009534__li_d35432e1_d35433e1_d35434e1\">With a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">run</span> statement used without a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/display</span> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/query</span> switch.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kax1665703009534__li_d35435e1_d35436e1_d35437e1\">With a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span> statement used with the component instance properties <code class=\"ph codeph\">DISPLAY=FALSE</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">QUERY=FALSE</code>.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kax1665703009534__li_d35438e1_d35439e1_d35440e1\">With an <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">activate</span> statement (resulting in an implicit <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span>).\n </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kax1665703009534__table_d9551e1_d9552e1_d9553e1__entry__1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kax1665703009534__table_d9551e1_d9552e1_d9553e1__entry__2\">\n The form can be used only for query purposes. All of these conditions are met:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kax1665703009534__li_d35441e1_d35442e1_d35443e1\">The form became active with an <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">edit</span> statement, or the exec operation is empty. in this case, Uniface behaves as if an <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">edit</span> statement were present.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kax1665703009534__li_d35444e1_d35445e1_d35446e1\">The form is a Limited form or the form was started by one of these methods:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kax1665703009534__li_d35447e1_d35448e1_d35449e1\">With a <code class=\"ph codeph\">run/query</code> statement.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kax1665703009534__li_d35450e1_d35451e1_d35452e1\">With a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span> statement used with the component instance property <code class=\"ph codeph\">QUERY=TRUE</code>.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kax1665703009534__table_d9551e1_d9552e1_d9553e1__entry__1\">\n 2\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kax1665703009534__table_d9551e1_d9552e1_d9553e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The form is display-only. One of these conditions is met:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kax1665703009534__li_d35453e1_d35454e1_d35455e1\">The form was started with a <code class=\"ph codeph\">run/display</code> statement.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kax1665703009534__li_d35456e1_d35457e1_d35458e1\">The form was started with a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span> statement used with the component instance property <code class=\"ph codeph\">DISPLAY=TRUE</code>.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kax1665703009534__li_d35459e1_d35460e1_d35461e1\">The form became active with a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">display</span> statement.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kax1665703009534__topic_d59052e1_d59053e1_d59054e1_d59055e1_d59056e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d490080e253\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kax1665703009534__p_d88670e1_d88671e1_d88672e1\">Allowed in Form components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kax1665703009534__topic_d59057e1_d59058e1_d59059e1_d59060e1_d59061e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d490080e263\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kax1665703009534__p_d88676e1_d88677e1_d88678e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$runmode</span> function returns a value that indicates how the form was started. This also indicates how the form can be used to affect data.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"kax1665703009534__note_w8826ab1b7c13b5_w8827ab1b7c13_w8828ab1b7_w8829ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The value of\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$runmode</span> can also be changed by\n            <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$editmode</span>.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kax1665703009534__section_ktz_d1h_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d490080e284\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$runmode</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">In this example, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$runmode</span> is used to inform the\n               user as to whether the form is editable or read-only.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"kax1665703009534__pre_p1r_21h_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation exec\nselectcase $runmode\n case 0\n message/info \"This form is editable\"\nelsecase\n message/info \"This form is not editable\"\n endselectcase\nedit\nend; exec</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oma1720015839839.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>display</a><p>Presents the form on the screen as display-only.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gwk1665702595783.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>edit</a><p>Display the component in preparation for user input.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5563551\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5563551\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$runmode (deprecated) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $runmode (deprecated) Return an indication of how the form was started. Important: The $runmode function has been superseded by $editmode . $runmode Return Values Table 1. Values returned by $runmode Value Meaning 0 The form can be used for all I/O purposes. All of these conditions are met: The form became active with an edit statement, or the exec operation is empty. in this case, Uniface behaves as if an edit statement were present. The form is not a Limited form. The form was started by one of these methods: With a run statement used without a /display or /query switch. With a newinstance statement used with the component instance properties DISPLAY=FALSE and QUERY=FALSE . With an activate statement (resulting in an implicit newinstance ). 1 The form can be used only for query purposes. All of these conditions are met: The form became active with an edit statement, or the exec operation is empty. in this case, Uniface behaves as if an edit statement were present. The form is a Limited form or the form was started by one of these methods: With a run/query statement. With a newinstance statement used with the component instance property QUERY=TRUE . 2 The form is display-only. One of these conditions is met: The form was started with a run/display statement. The form was started with a newinstance statement used with the component instance property DISPLAY=TRUE . The form became active with a display statement. Use Allowed in Form components. Description The $runmode function returns a value that indicates how the form was started. This also indicates how the form can be used to affect data. Note: The value of $runmode can also be changed by $editmode . Example: Using $runmode In this example, $runmode is used to inform the user as to whether the form is editable or read-only. operation exec selectcase $runmode case 0 message/info \"This form is editable\" elsecase message/info \"This form is not editable\" endselectcase edit end; exec Copy Related Links display Presents the form on the screen as display-only. edit Display the component in preparation for user input. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}